00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:04,680
It sounds destructive, but mathematically collapse is the ultimate act of reconstruction.

367
00:26:05,380 --> 00:26:11,760
Collapse is the operator that forces the system to calculate where it currently is based entirely on what it has done.

