00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,400
Or the start of the program.

374
00:26:27,540 --> 00:26:28,000
Exactly.

375
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:39,880
Now, in the calculus of sphere pop, for every possible element X that you could ever pop from the option space, there is a corresponding state transformation mathematical function.

376
00:26:40,020 --> 00:26:41,420
Let's call it T sub X.

