00:28:48,760 --> 00:28:51,860
The state you see is just a shadow cast by the history.

403
00:28:51,860 --> 00:28:54,820
That is a flawless translation of the mathematics.

404
00:28:55,640 --> 00:29:00,060
The observable state is always a derived object computed on demand.

405
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:06,360
This total inversion treating history as the primary unchangeable bedrock of reality,

