00:32:22,360 --> 00:32:24,940
Italian over Mexican is a preference.

463
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:26,780
It is a structural refusal.

464
00:32:27,280 --> 00:32:32,520
And this idea of tracking the cost of actions leads directly into what is arguably the most

465
00:32:32,520 --> 00:32:35,900
intimidating, physics-heavy section of the papers.

466
00:32:36,580 --> 00:32:39,520
The discrete Lagrangian mechanics of commitment.

